title: Freak Power-The Fried Funk Food EP
description:
320 Kbit/s mp3 Original CD Rip,

I remember that this was an bonus EP that came with the first issue of their regular "drive through booty" album. Whatever about the main album the bonus cd is amazing, easily the best thing I have ever heard. I have tried to find anything similiar to this but have failed. I am an old pothead and only imagine that this is something modern called "dope beatz" or ambient or something like that - I don't know. I think it is just fantastic. It is in my mind the ultimate chill out album. If you see it get it - beg, borrow or steal. I actually think it is better than the main album and I know it is the only decent bonus cd I have ever bought.
